{"tid":1847213,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"1128: 明天起政府僱員可在家工作 私人機構可作出類似安排","createTime":"2020-01-28T03:32:41.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-28T05:00:05.000Z","uid":22556,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"788f2d587bc2cfd86bfd9a9ee3b1b60ccfc50c0d","tid":1847213,"uid":22556,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-28T03:32:41.000Z","msg":"政府部門特別上班安排<br />\n＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊<br />\n　　為了盡量減低疫情在社區擴散的風險，政府發言人今日（一月二十八日）宣布，政府部門將會於農曆新年假期後（即一月二十九日起）實施特別上班安排。除了提供緊急和必須公共服務的人員外，政府僱員在假期後無需返回寫字樓辦公，而是留在家中工作。<br />\n<br />\n　　有關安排暫定實行至二月二日，政府屆時會再檢視情況。<br />\n<br />\n　　政府發言人呼籲私人機構在可行情況下，作類似安排。<br />\n<br />\n　　個別政府部門會就受影響的公共服務作出公布。 <br />\n <br />\n完<br />\n2020年1月28日（星期二）<br />\n香港時間11時20分"},{"pid":"cab345fa99abeaa3d4d2fe0f05f4a4d37168fd48","tid":1847213,"uid":1441,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-28T03:33:32.000Z","msg":"link 呢?"},{"pid":"268ea441bffaf9e1cbb1a88c6eda729f28afd087","tid":1847213,"uid":55941,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-28T03:33:40.000Z","msg":"公務員先有<br />\n其他港豬等死啦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"062b69aa617aeef3067e2d920689ff252ad18c60","tid":1847213,"uid":215734,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-28T03:34:28.000Z","msg":"呼籲<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/clown3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/clown3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/clown3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"71a3a50f9ce4f37cd7ee84be22b4cef63f694f7b","tid":1847213,"uid":22556,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"cab345fa99abeaa3d4d2fe0f05f4a4d37168fd48","tid":1847213,"uid":1441,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-28T03:33:32.000Z","msg":"link 呢?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-28T03:37:09.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.info.gov.h